\r\n三、服用毒品、麻醉藥品或其他相類之物，致不能安全駕駛。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/ULDM/110%2c%e8%99%8e%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c19%2c20210218%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"ULDM,110,虎交簡,19,20210218,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"虎交簡","JNO":"19","JDATE":"20210218","JTITLE":"公共危險"}